ion than something essential for answering questions about current capabilities, so I'll leave it out.\n\nI'm also verifying the other details: the source includes reference links and release categories that the knowledge file doesn't list separately, but merging them into the descriptions seems appropriate. Item 5 about the batch file deletion is correctly documented with its reasoning. Everything checks out.\n\nSo I've found just two minor issues: a typo where \"Policy\" is misspelled as \"Politcy,\" and one missing reference to nablarch-single-module-archetype in the hints. Otherwise the knowledge file is solid and accurate.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":21648,"cache_read_input_tokens":18400,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":21648,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":8},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8cc32aee-f7be-4ba6-af58-a8b4dfe6f596","uuid":"197e5135-cdd0-4611-a073-030f0876c266"}
